This directory contains the packaging files for various kteam-tools libraries,
files and utilities.


Build a package
===============

Install the build frontend (one-time setup)
$ pip3 install build

Build - for example - the ckt-cranky package
$ cd ckt-cranky
$ python3 -m build


Install a package (from source)
===============================

Create a virtual environment (one-time setup)
$ python3 -m venv venv

Enter the virtual environment
$ . venv/bin/activate

Install - for example - the ckt-info package into the virtual environment
$ cd ckt-info
$ pip3 install .

Leave the virtual environment
$ deactivate
